                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Bāznāmah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa">بازنامه</title>
                     <note>"An anonymous treatise on falconry in verse, the date of composition of which is indicated by the chronogram (= 1050/1640-1), which is inscribed on the fly leaf (ترمتی). The poem, which is copied from a faulty archetype, is dedicated to Shah Shuja', presumably Shahjahan's son (d. 1071/1661). The author states that he wrote the work at the instance of a certain Shaikh Hasan"</note>
